56d76e2d50a20472e26aed22db48b9bcf5ea001e237976dd9b39900e409591a085fae8205162ed0f1cc63f9c37b59bf7af10a156755a0c067d42fcaab8e3c589  0001-Use-cargo-auditable-build-instead-of-cargo-build.patch
